696
00:38:43,724 --> 00:38:44,863
¡No hagas eso!
¡He dicho que pares!

697
00:38:44,894 --> 00:38:45,853
Quando fiet.

698
00:38:45,894 --> 00:38:46,653
¿Qué has dicho?

699
00:38:46,654 --> 00:38:49,493
No lo sé. Oigo voces.

700
00:38:49,524 --> 00:38:50,663
Una hora...

701
00:38:50,664 --> 00:38:52,363
...Locum statuisti.

702
00:38:52,364 --> 00:38:53,533
Creo que es latín.

703
00:38:53,534 --> 00:38:55,133
