704
00:38:55,514 --> 00:38:56,613
Joder, ¿qué palabra es?

705
00:38:56,614 --> 00:38:58,783
Hora, hora.

706
00:38:59,174 --> 00:39:00,793
Algo va a pasar en una hora.

707
00:39:00,864 --> 00:39:02,933
